{"tw": {"2755480": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "社群審查 DX", "steam_appid": 2755480, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "dlc": [3985140, 3985240], "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🔽故事簡介🔽</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成天在家裡無所事事的悠斗是個電腦天才與偶像宅。儘管有些不甘願，但為了生計，還是在接到社群平台Facibook的邀請後，成為了審查情色內容的社群審查員，負責將違反社群規範的圖片Ban掉。沒想到乏味無聊的審查工作，竟然讓他發現了公寓管理員人妻美沙、最愛的偶像優衣、還有教會的修女梨花她們不為人知的秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >同一時間，悠斗也發現當他在工作上犯錯，將情色內容不小心流出，公寓周遭的人們以及電視上播報的新聞內容似乎漸漸開始有一些不對勁。好像整個社會的道德界線變得混亂，大家越來越性開放…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/e21e7cbe1f214a6fd6381c57671a336e.avif?t=1776625058\" width=800 height=432 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🔽遊戲內容🔽</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在每天的四個時段一邊工作賺錢提升職等，一邊探索城市與NPC對話。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/1196ec8bc67a432e236e8c9c910dc77d.avif?t=1776625058\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/566cef820dc274aac0ab5ceec3183b92.poster.avif?t=1776625058\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/566cef820dc274aac0ab5ceec3183b92.webm?t=1776625058\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/566cef820dc274aac0ab5ceec3183b92.mp4?t=1776625058\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/84bf352fd5e71fdf32c5543d35ae508e.poster.avif?t=1776625058\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/84bf352fd5e71fdf32c5543d35ae508e.webm?t=1776625058\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/84bf352fd5e71fdf32c5543d35ae508e.mp4?t=1776625058\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >社群審查員總共有5個職等，從實習生、初級雇員、中級雇員、高級雇員、管理員。當工作表現優異，獲得足夠的經驗值，就可以升等獲得更高的薪水，與更高的自由度。這代表你開始可以在工作上「不小心」犯錯，流出一些情色內容來提升社會的「混亂度」，而不會立刻被開除。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隨著混沌值的上升，NPC將開始展現更多異常行為，可以解鎖新的色情事件，台詞與服裝也可能產生改變。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/f12413e5e08f09e42a28e213f8b33b1b.avif?t=1776625058\" width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/826dd53b4e5aa050b9c18eab265694b0.poster.avif?t=1776625058\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/826dd53b4e5aa050b9c18eab265694b0.webm?t=1776625058\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/826dd53b4e5aa050b9c18eab265694b0.mp4?t=1776625058\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成功攻略管理員美沙後，便利商店購買「公車卡」，可以開啟教堂、漫展、警局等新地圖和豐富的小遊戲供探索，以及偶像美沙、修女梨花兩個可供略角色。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/b860871737624ebe1cbf38eb646af2b7.avif?t=1776625058\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/7887a0ca814e5921af6499dc4ce3d299.avif?t=1776625058\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/8a67856c4a760d33d59ea0ecdbfa54d0.avif?t=1776625058\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最新版也包含DLC內容，新增新的攻略對象「女主播」。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🔽遊戲玩法🔽</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每天分為早上、下午、晚上、午夜四個時段，每個時段可選擇不同行動，如工作賺錢、探索地圖與NPC對話等，自由度相當高。隨著遊戲的進行，可以探索的地區和可以互動的角色會越來越多。每個時段會出現的NPC和可以玩的小遊戲也會有變化，增加探索的樂趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >透過社群審查的工作，與女主角們互動。同時一邊提升職等，一邊提高世界的混亂度。並透過一連串的小遊戲，嘗試不同的體位和場景，增加和女主角的親密度。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/22a36b1d5bf3e9d1383191fc4edc3b4c.poster.avif?t=1776625058\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/22a36b1d5bf3e9d1383191fc4edc3b4c.webm?t=1776625058\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/22a36b1d5bf3e9d1383191fc4edc3b4c.mp4?t=1776625058\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >教堂和漫展也有各自的任務和極其豐富的小遊戲。在教堂裡不斷和不同NPC對話，參與懺悔</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >和唱詩和修女拉近關係，發現教堂隱藏的淫亂。在漫展為了獲得和偶像優衣獨處的機會，必需通過所有攤位的考驗，集滿印章。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/63d8a61be06e3bdfd36ef93efb8f8ad5.poster.avif?t=1776625058\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/63d8a61be06e3bdfd36ef93efb8f8ad5.webm?t=1776625058\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/63d8a61be06e3bdfd36ef93efb8f8ad5.mp4?t=1776625058\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/8ce31409f3c4332bf7e777f9015b4de8.poster.avif?t=1776625058\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/8ce31409f3c4332bf7e777f9015b4de8.webm?t=1776625058\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/8ce31409f3c4332bf7e777f9015b4de8.mp4?t=1776625058\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/c77a6972adcf9dfb826f09137997e370.poster.avif?t=1776625058\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/c77a6972adcf9dfb826f09137997e370.webm?t=1776625058\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/c77a6972adcf9dfb826f09137997e370.mp4?t=1776625058\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/7ae657de82ed6bfb1358d5108c0a8fc1.poster.avif?t=1776625058\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/7ae657de82ed6bfb1358d5108c0a8fc1.webm?t=1776625058\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/7ae657de82ed6bfb1358d5108c0a8fc1.mp4?t=1776625058\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🔽人物介紹🔽</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/43044a0cfdd3c7430b73cb7ee20e9215.avif?t=1776625058\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&lt;聲優&gt;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Maria Ayana: 米沙, 優衣</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Megumu Morino: 梨花, 百合子(DLC更新)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🔽遊戲特色🔽</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >●12種以上多樣豐富的小遊戲與任務。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >●超過60枚點陣圖動畫，與200個以上的差分。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >●共有三個主要場景，超過30個NPC。絕大部分的女性NPC均可攻略。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >●《NTR狂熱》中的千穗與莉莉絲，以及許多由芒果派對發行的人氣遊戲中的角色都會以彩蛋的形式登場。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/da4be55d4b3d3e500dc02722cdcbc676.avif?t=1776625058\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※遊戲中出現的其他遊戲的角色與CG圖，均已獲得開發者同意授權。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※v4.0.13 更新。遊戲支援全滑鼠操控遊玩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-滑鼠右鍵移動人物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-滑鼠左鍵按鈕確認。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/c52f385f01e89218e6c1424f5ba850cc.poster.avif?t=1776625058\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/c52f385f01e89218e6c1424f5ba850cc.webm?t=1776625058\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/c52f385f01e89218e6c1424f5ba850cc.mp4?t=1776625058\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🔽故事簡介🔽</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成天在家裡無所事事的悠斗是個電腦天才與偶像宅。儘管有些不甘願，但為了生計，還是在接到社群平台Facibook的邀請後，成為了審查情色內容的社群審查員，負責將違反社群規範的圖片Ban掉。沒想到乏味無聊的審查工作，竟然讓他發現了公寓管理員人妻美沙、最愛的偶像優衣、還有教會的修女梨花她們不為人知的秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >同一時間，悠斗也發現當他在工作上犯錯，將情色內容不小心流出，公寓周遭的人們以及電視上播報的新聞內容似乎漸漸開始有一些不對勁。好像整個社會的道德界線變得混亂，大家越來越性開放…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/e21e7cbe1f214a6fd6381c57671a336e.avif?t=1776625058\" width=800 height=432 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🔽遊戲內容🔽</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在每天的四個時段一邊工作賺錢提升職等，一邊探索城市與NPC對話。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/1196ec8bc67a432e236e8c9c910dc77d.avif?t=1776625058\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/566cef820dc274aac0ab5ceec3183b92.poster.avif?t=1776625058\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/566cef820dc274aac0ab5ceec3183b92.webm?t=1776625058\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/566cef820dc274aac0ab5ceec3183b92.mp4?t=1776625058\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/84bf352fd5e71fdf32c5543d35ae508e.poster.avif?t=1776625058\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/84bf352fd5e71fdf32c5543d35ae508e.webm?t=1776625058\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/84bf352fd5e71fdf32c5543d35ae508e.mp4?t=1776625058\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >社群審查員總共有5個職等，從實習生、初級雇員、中級雇員、高級雇員、管理員。當工作表現優異，獲得足夠的經驗值，就可以升等獲得更高的薪水，與更高的自由度。這代表你開始可以在工作上「不小心」犯錯，流出一些情色內容來提升社會的「混亂度」，而不會立刻被開除。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隨著混沌值的上升，NPC將開始展現更多異常行為，可以解鎖新的色情事件，台詞與服裝也可能產生改變。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/f12413e5e08f09e42a28e213f8b33b1b.avif?t=1776625058\" width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/826dd53b4e5aa050b9c18eab265694b0.poster.avif?t=1776625058\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/826dd53b4e5aa050b9c18eab265694b0.webm?t=1776625058\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/826dd53b4e5aa050b9c18eab265694b0.mp4?t=1776625058\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成功攻略管理員美沙後，便利商店購買「公車卡」，可以開啟教堂、漫展、警局等新地圖和豐富的小遊戲供探索，以及偶像美沙、修女梨花兩個可供略角色。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/b860871737624ebe1cbf38eb646af2b7.avif?t=1776625058\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/7887a0ca814e5921af6499dc4ce3d299.avif?t=1776625058\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/8a67856c4a760d33d59ea0ecdbfa54d0.avif?t=1776625058\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最新版也包含DLC內容，新增新的攻略對象「女主播」。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🔽遊戲玩法🔽</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每天分為早上、下午、晚上、午夜四個時段，每個時段可選擇不同行動，如工作賺錢、探索地圖與NPC對話等，自由度相當高。隨著遊戲的進行，可以探索的地區和可以互動的角色會越來越多。每個時段會出現的NPC和可以玩的小遊戲也會有變化，增加探索的樂趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >透過社群審查的工作，與女主角們互動。同時一邊提升職等，一邊提高世界的混亂度。並透過一連串的小遊戲，嘗試不同的體位和場景，增加和女主角的親密度。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/22a36b1d5bf3e9d1383191fc4edc3b4c.poster.avif?t=1776625058\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/22a36b1d5bf3e9d1383191fc4edc3b4c.webm?t=1776625058\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/22a36b1d5bf3e9d1383191fc4edc3b4c.mp4?t=1776625058\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >教堂和漫展也有各自的任務和極其豐富的小遊戲。在教堂裡不斷和不同NPC對話，參與懺悔</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >和唱詩和修女拉近關係，發現教堂隱藏的淫亂。在漫展為了獲得和偶像優衣獨處的機會，必需通過所有攤位的考驗，集滿印章。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/63d8a61be06e3bdfd36ef93efb8f8ad5.poster.avif?t=1776625058\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/63d8a61be06e3bdfd36ef93efb8f8ad5.webm?t=1776625058\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/63d8a61be06e3bdfd36ef93efb8f8ad5.mp4?t=1776625058\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/8ce31409f3c4332bf7e777f9015b4de8.poster.avif?t=1776625058\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/8ce31409f3c4332bf7e777f9015b4de8.webm?t=1776625058\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/8ce31409f3c4332bf7e777f9015b4de8.mp4?t=1776625058\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/c77a6972adcf9dfb826f09137997e370.poster.avif?t=1776625058\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/c77a6972adcf9dfb826f09137997e370.webm?t=1776625058\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/c77a6972adcf9dfb826f09137997e370.mp4?t=1776625058\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/7ae657de82ed6bfb1358d5108c0a8fc1.poster.avif?t=1776625058\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/7ae657de82ed6bfb1358d5108c0a8fc1.webm?t=1776625058\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/7ae657de82ed6bfb1358d5108c0a8fc1.mp4?t=1776625058\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🔽人物介紹🔽</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/43044a0cfdd3c7430b73cb7ee20e9215.avif?t=1776625058\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&lt;聲優&gt;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Maria Ayana: 米沙, 優衣</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Megumu Morino: 梨花, 百合子(DLC更新)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🔽遊戲特色🔽</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >●12種以上多樣豐富的小遊戲與任務。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >●超過60枚點陣圖動畫，與200個以上的差分。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >●共有三個主要場景，超過30個NPC。絕大部分的女性NPC均可攻略。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >●《NTR狂熱》中的千穗與莉莉絲，以及許多由芒果派對發行的人氣遊戲中的角色都會以彩蛋的形式登場。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/da4be55d4b3d3e500dc02722cdcbc676.avif?t=1776625058\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※遊戲中出現的其他遊戲的角色與CG圖，均已獲得開發者同意授權。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※v4.0.13 更新。遊戲支援全滑鼠操控遊玩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-滑鼠右鍵移動人物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-滑鼠左鍵按鈕確認。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/c52f385f01e89218e6c1424f5ba850cc.poster.avif?t=1776625058\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/c52f385f01e89218e6c1424f5ba850cc.webm?t=1776625058\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/c52f385f01e89218e6c1424f5ba850cc.mp4?t=1776625058\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>", "short_description": "成天在家裡無所事事的悠斗是個電腦天才與偶像宅。儘管有些不甘願，但為了生計，還是成為了社群平台Facibook負責審查情色內容的社群審查員。沒想到乏味無聊的審查工作，竟然讓他發現了公寓管理員人妻美沙、最愛的偶像優衣、還有教會的修女梨花她們不為人知的秘密。", "supported_languages": "英文, 日文<strong>*</strong>, 韓文, 俄文, 簡體中文, 繁體中文<br><strong>*</strong>具備完整音效支援的語言", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/4c49a2fcdff935e2d11cd4d08607df529789b923/header_tchinese.jpg?t=1776625058", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/c94defa346f71d688b0033de61443d6896e57e1f/capsule_231x87_tchinese.jpg?t=1776625058", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/c94defa346f71d688b0033de61443d6896e57e1f/capsule_184x69_tchinese.jpg?t=1776625058", "website": "https://x.com/tiramisuloventr", "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統 *:</strong> Windows 7 64bit OS<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Core i3<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 4 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> Nvidia GTX 650 Ti<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 2 GB 可用空間</li></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統:</strong> Windows 10 64bit OS<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Core i5<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 8 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> Nvidia GTX 650 Ti<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 2 GB 可用空間</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": [], "linux_requirements": [], "legal_notice": "All characters are above 18.", "developers": ["Tiramisu", "Big S Studio"], "publishers": ["Mango Party", "Mango Party News"], "price_overview": {"currency": "TWD", "initial": 31900, "final": 28700, "discount_percent": 10, "initial_formatted": "NT$ 319", "final_formatted": "NT$ 287"}, "categories": [{"id": 2, "description": "單人"}, {"id": 23, "description": "Steam 雲端"}, {"id": 62, "description": "親友同享"}], "genres": [{"id": "4", "description": "休閒"}, {"id": "23", "description": "獨立製作"}, {"id": "28", "description": "模擬"}], "release_date": {"coming_soon": false, "date": "2025 年 9 月 18 日"}}}}, "us": {"2755480": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "The Censor DX Edition", "steam_appid": 2755480, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "dlc": [3985140, 3985240], "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/f4141ebe70e4b7182357d9d45ab95b3c.avif?t=1776625058\" width=1560 height=1040 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🔽Story🔽</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Yuto Fujimoto is a shut-in with a knack for computers and an unhealthy obsession with idols. When Facibook offers him a job censoring adult content, he takes it reluctantly, spending his days scrubbing images that violate community guidelines.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At first, the work is mind-numbing. However, as the flagged posts pile up, Yuto starts noticing something strange. Behind the filters and file names lie hidden connections to three women in his life: Misa, the married apartment manager. Yui, his favorite idol. And Rika, the pious nun at the local church. All of them are harboring secrets he never expected to uncover.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What starts as a mundane job takes a wild turn when Yuto mistakenly lets adult content slip past moderation. The strange reactions from his neighbors and the media suggest something's changed...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/e21e7cbe1f214a6fd6381c57671a336e.avif?t=1776625058\" width=800 height=432 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🔽Game Overview🔽</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each day is split into four time slots, giving you time to earn money, rise through the ranks, and explore the city while deepening your connections with NPCs. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/1196ec8bc67a432e236e8c9c910dc77d.avif?t=1776625058\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/566cef820dc274aac0ab5ceec3183b92.poster.avif?t=1776625058\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/566cef820dc274aac0ab5ceec3183b92.webm?t=1776625058\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/566cef820dc274aac0ab5ceec3183b92.mp4?t=1776625058\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/84bf352fd5e71fdf32c5543d35ae508e.poster.avif?t=1776625058\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/84bf352fd5e71fdf32c5543d35ae508e.webm?t=1776625058\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/84bf352fd5e71fdf32c5543d35ae508e.mp4?t=1776625058\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’ll progress through five ranks, from Intern to Manager, unlocking better pay and greater freedom with each promotion. With that freedom comes opportunity: once you’ve proven yourself, you can start making “mistakes” on purpose, letting explicit content slip through to quietly raise the world’s CHAOS level without getting fired for it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the world slips deeper into chaos, the NPCs begin to behave in unexpected and perverse ways. Dialogue shifts, outfits change, and new lewd events are unlocked.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/f12413e5e08f09e42a28e213f8b33b1b.avif?t=1776625058\" width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/826dd53b4e5aa050b9c18eab265694b0.poster.avif?t=1776625058\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/826dd53b4e5aa050b9c18eab265694b0.webm?t=1776625058\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/826dd53b4e5aa050b9c18eab265694b0.mp4?t=1776625058\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Conquer Misa Hashimoto’s route to buy a bus card at the convenience store. This opens up the Church, Convention, and Police Station—each packed with new content and minigames.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/b860871737624ebe1cbf38eb646af2b7.avif?t=1776625058\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/7887a0ca814e5921af6499dc4ce3d299.avif?t=1776625058\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/8a67856c4a760d33d59ea0ecdbfa54d0.avif?t=1776625058\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The newest update includes all DLC, featuring a fresh new target of desire.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🔽Game Play🔽</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every day consists of four periods—Morning, Afternoon, Evening and Night. Plan your schedule wisely to boost relationships, earn cash, and uncover secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find opportunities to get closer to the heroine. Rank up as a censor and keep driving the world further into chaos!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/22a36b1d5bf3e9d1383191fc4edc3b4c.poster.avif?t=1776625058\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/22a36b1d5bf3e9d1383191fc4edc3b4c.webm?t=1776625058\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/22a36b1d5bf3e9d1383191fc4edc3b4c.mp4?t=1776625058\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique missions and mini-games await at both the Church and the Convention. Engage in confessionals, sing hymns, or dive into the more depraved side of religious devotion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/63d8a61be06e3bdfd36ef93efb8f8ad5.poster.avif?t=1776625058\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/63d8a61be06e3bdfd36ef93efb8f8ad5.webm?t=1776625058\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/63d8a61be06e3bdfd36ef93efb8f8ad5.mp4?t=1776625058\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/8ce31409f3c4332bf7e777f9015b4de8.poster.avif?t=1776625058\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/8ce31409f3c4332bf7e777f9015b4de8.webm?t=1776625058\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/8ce31409f3c4332bf7e777f9015b4de8.mp4?t=1776625058\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/c77a6972adcf9dfb826f09137997e370.poster.avif?t=1776625058\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/c77a6972adcf9dfb826f09137997e370.webm?t=1776625058\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/c77a6972adcf9dfb826f09137997e370.mp4?t=1776625058\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/7ae657de82ed6bfb1358d5108c0a8fc1.poster.avif?t=1776625058\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755480/extras/7ae657de82ed6bfb1358d5108c0a8fc1.webm?t=1776625058\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/